## SUMMARY

**Single Factory Pipeline**: Discovery → Demand Validation → Build → Scale

**System of Record**: Cursor (all docs, code, decisions, checklists)

**Tool Lanes**: No overlap, single purpose per tool

**Global Gates**: Discovery Score ≥ 8.0, Validation Thresholds pass, Feature Flags required, Multi-tenancy enforced

**Mandatory Outputs**: 5 discovery docs, 7 validation docs, 7 build docs per idea/feature

**Orchestration**: Single Orchestrator agent runs steps in order, calls specialist agents, enforces gates, produces decisions, maintains checklists

**This creates a predictable, repeatable factory for building SaaS products.**
